    "date": "2021-07-16T14:20:01Z",
    "text": "Apprenticeship Hubs Across America Act of 2021\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Labor to implement a program to award grants to workforce intermediaries (certain national, regional, state, or local entities that facilitate the establishment of registered apprenticeship programs) to enable them to engage a variety of stakeholders to support, develop, and implement registered apprenticeship programs."
